  _missions:
  - Act: 2
    QuestId: cottagesReopen
    Title: Two Boards Come Down
    Summary: Keep the restoration ledger and fund the first new shutters.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: festivalHosted
    Title: The First Festival in Three Years
    Summary: Record the season's public turning point.
  _quotes:
  - Text: The Wenmar house wants shutters more than it wants sympathy.
    Context: Explaining the next restoration cost.
  - Text: Two shutters is a sentence beginning.
    Context: Recording the first reopened cottages.
  - Text: This year's page may need more ink.
    Context: Watching the festival preparations.
